            Nigerian special effects makeup artist on creating gore for Nollywood
            Hakeem Effects is an award-winning special effects makeup artist working in Nollywood. He creates, zombies, blood and gore for the multi-billion dollar Nigerian film industry, which produces thousands of films every year. Video journalist: Sarah Tiamiyu forBBC News Pidgin
                
